metadata.name: The Cry for Freedom
metadata.description:
Every rotten peace has an active war stuck fighting in it.

This is for all those who fight for their freedom.  
For all those who are left alone in their battle.  
For all those who have to watch hopelessly.  
For all who have to endure powerlessly.

This is my cry.

_____  
Finalist of the "AI Art Contest 3" by Claire Silver.
